Great news â€” on **.NET 10 SDK**, `dotnet test` has **native MTP support**, so you **no longer need `TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport`**. That property was only required for .NET 9 and earlier.

### Setup

Add a `test` section to your **`global.json`**:

```json
{
  "sdk": {
    "version": "10.0.100"
  },
  "test": {
    "runner": "Microsoft.Testing.Platform"
  }
}
```

